                                                    are obsessed with rolli=
ng down this endless digital slope!
                                                </p>

                                                <h2><strong>How To Play Slo=
pe Game</strong></h2>

                                                <div class=3D"how-to-play-i=
ntro">
                                                    <p>
                                                        <strong>Slope Game<=
/strong> is elegantly simple to control but
                                                        incredibly challeng=
ing to master.
                                                        The core gameplay r=
evolves around steering a ball down an
                                                        endless slope while=
 avoiding obstacles.
                                                        However, as your sp=
eed increases and the track becomes more
                                                        complex, split-seco=
nd decisions
                                                        and precise movemen=
ts become the difference between success and
                                                        failure.
                                                    </p>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class=3D"how-to-play-g=
rid">
                                                    <div class=3D"how-to-pl=
ay-box">
                                                        <h3><strong>Control=
s</strong></h3>
                                                        <ul>
                                                            <li><strong>Arr=
ow Keys / A/D:</strong> Steer your glowing
                                                                sphere left=
 and right as it races down the slope with
                                                                instant, re=
sponsive control.</li>
                                                            <li><strong>Smo=
oth Steering:</strong> Use gentle, gradual
                                                                movements r=
ather than sharp turns - the ball's physics
                                                                respond bet=
ter to precise adjustments at high speeds.
